Provides support classes for DLIC and DLICGenerator.

    RandomGridIterator_DensityDependent  
    RandomGridIterator_Original
    RandomGridIterator: Iterates over an integer, rectangular grid in a pseudo-random order Because it is difficult to quickly produce a fully random ordering of all the grid points, this class uses a pseudo-random technique: The grid is divided evenly into square blocks, and a random point is chosen in the top-left block.
